Useful resources to get started in phaser and learn the documentation

Phaser documentaion for phaser version 2.7 community edition
https://photonstorm.github.io/phaser-ce/

A website to observe and experiment with common game mechanics and how they can be created with Phaser
https://gamemechanicexplorer.com/#

A tutorial for the menu that we are following
https://github.com/MattMcFarland/phaser-menu-system
